vote.title:
A public hearing to receive comments regarding an application for and an ordinance granting the creation of a new Special Provision Sign District (SPSD) on property containing the Wynnewood Village Shopping Center, to be known as the Wynnewood Village Sign District and zoned Regional Retail District (RR), on the northwest corner of West Illinois Avenue and South Zang Boulevard
Recommendation of Staff:  Approval, subject to conditions
Recommendation of CPC:  Approval, subject to conditions
SPSD223-001(JP)
